Reactive Supply and Voltage Control from Generation Sources Service
Brunner Island, LLC ( Brunner Island ) provides Reactive Supply and Voltage Control from Generation Sources Service ( Reactive Supply Service ) from various generating units in the PPL Zone to the PJM Interconnection, L.L.C. ( PJM ). This Rate Schedule consists of three separate tariff rate sections, one for each generating unit, and sets forth Brunner Island s revenue requirements for the provision of Reactive Supply Service to PJM within the PPL Zone consistent with Schedule 2 of the PJM Open Access Transmission Tariff. This Rate Schedule shall be effective on such date as established by the Federal Energy Regulatory Commission.
BRUNNER ISLAND 1
1. TOTAL REVENUE REQUIREMENT
Total Annual Revenue Requirement is $751,778.35.
Total Monthly Revenue Requirement is $751,778.35 / 12 = $62,648.20.
BRUNNER ISLAND 2
1. TOTAL REVENUE REQUIREMENT
Total Annual Revenue Requirement is $696,261.22.
Total Monthly Revenue Requirement is $696,261.22 / 12 = $58,021.77.
BRUNNER ISLAND 3
1. TOTAL REVENUE REQUIREMENT
Total Annual Revenue Requirement is $346,671.37.
Total Monthly Revenue Requirement is $346,671.37 / 12 = $28,889.28.
